{"tid":2340894,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"驚世大發現！原來《傾城》歌詞可以完美填入《Lonely Christmas》嘅旋律","createTime":"2020-12-26T01:45:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T04:06:51.000Z","uid":101392,"like":24,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7101f8cfc0d3389cced74d2d56c79f0a4de705b3","tid":2340894,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T01:45:45.000Z","msg":"誰熱情在此即使熄了<br />\n而別離夜晚也極緊要<br />\n甜蜜與嬉笑 真與假的也給我吧<br />\n要記住決不減少<br />\n<br />\n繁盛寒夜中 燈光普照<br />\n而話題盡了也沒緊要<br />\n唇上那一吻 淒冷深宵這都市內<br />\n與你亦再沒破曉<br />\n<br />\n傳說 這紅眼睛<br />\n淚眼 這城已傾<br />\n如像擠出的苦笑臉<br />\n盛世充當分手佈景<br />\n<br />\n傳說 這紅眼睛<br />\n淚眼 世情冷清<br />\n停下笙歌 煙花會謝<br />\n但卻終章 偏偏要傾聽<br />\n<br />\n瓊樓玉宇 絕世風景<br />\n全城為我都花光狠勁<br />\n如同在傻笑　換到那癡心淚眼睛 <br />\n霓虹滅了 漸覺淒清 <br />\n紅紅淚眼睛 幽幽傾訴<br />\n浮華夜城市 絕世中傾倒看不到"},{"pid":"4564ba5dae113be08dd7fb2b9f3025bab65c54ee","tid":2340894,"uid":101392,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T01:46:02.000Z","msg":"（<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尋晚過住Lonely Christmas <br />\n聽到傾城同Lonely Christmas <br />\n即刻覺得個feel好似 <br />\n同埋歌詞好match<br />\n通宵填咗好耐 求狠評）"},{"pid":"0ba31d11a7b0e6af0d1466823593ab725d12cb1e","tid":2340894,"uid":28971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T01:47:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f17f1819f70e05f41a09838bb59efa26540b5d6a","tid":2340894,"uid":25260,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T01:48:51.000Z","msg":"要你改就唔係完美填入啦"},{"pid":"1ff836c5338e3737e79c0e68a5ae6b7e069f282c","tid":2340894,"uid":101392,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T01:50:11.000Z","msg":"平時Lonely Christmas 都係喺個人層面覺得自己孤單<br />\n但係今年Lonely Christmas提升咗一個層次<br />\n係成個城市已經被國安法摧毀<br />\n好友、伴侶紛紛移民<br />\n所以好有傾城歌詞嘅Feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"217ca0b8a693782ac986b154246542d5660f7ac7","tid":2340894,"uid":45350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T01:50:20.000Z","msg":"唱黎聽下"},{"pid":"ca4c4023ecfc13c6b3f26f9bd5153dc1c3476241","tid":2340894,"uid":101392,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f17f1819f70e05f41a09838bb59efa26540b5d6a","tid":2340894,"uid":25260,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T01:48:51.000Z","msg":"要你改就唔係完美填入啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T01:50:38.000Z","msg":"標題黨嚟姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實都諗左好耐"},{"pid":"c787d1a05ffbdec160281d6aaef0a5ee1b177b89","tid":2340894,"uid":28641,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T01:51:32.000Z","msg":"On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0997bb7161ab072e8cc96411ab310bbd11db0f0","tid":2340894,"uid":101392,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T01:55:44.000Z","msg":"呢首新版Lonely Christmas <br />\n記載20年代國安法下人心惶惶、移民潮下嘅聖誕<br />\n應該可以同埋記載90年代8964後、移民潮下聖誕嘅《今天應該很高興》並列<br />\n載入香港史書<br />\n作為時代嘅一個紀錄"},{"pid":"08db0111dd951620cd68e286935dbd660d11773b","tid":2340894,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T01:57:41.000Z","msg":"當年Wyman嘅《傾城》都係記載主權移交下一個城市嘅滅亡<br />\n今日呢首新版《傾城》就可以喺每年聖誕同埋舊版互相呼應"},{"pid":"552c7c23f79381ae8e0a5e768409b36d8cec4f6b","tid":2340894,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"c787d1a05ffbdec160281d6aaef0a5ee1b177b89","tid":2340894,"uid":28641,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T01:51:32.000Z","msg":"On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20